# MEND-HD Master Dataset Construction

This folder contains the R Markdown file used to build the 14-day master dataset.

## Required Files

To run this script locally, place the following files in the same directory:

- Date_RangesMF0303.xlsx
- subjectdaystats.csv
- activity_*.csv
- heartrate_*.csv
- sleepmetrics*.csv

Raw data files are not stored in this repository.

## Output

Running the R Markdown file will generate:

- Master_Data_03_03_26.xlsx

To view the rendered report, download the HTML file and open locally.
